flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> Input[/User Request/]
    Input --> Auth{Authenticated?}
    Auth -->|No| Login[Login Page]
    Login --> Validate{Valid Credentials?}
    Validate -->|No| Error[Show Error]
    Error --> Login
    Validate -->|Yes| Auth
    Auth -->|Yes| Route{Route Type}
    Route -->|API| RateLimit{Rate Limited?}
    RateLimit -->|Yes| TooMany[429 Too Many Requests]
    RateLimit -->|No| Process[Process Request]
    Route -->|Static| Cache{In Cache?}
    Cache -->|Yes| Serve[Serve from Cache]
    Cache -->|No| Generate[Generate Response]
    Generate --> Store[(Store in Cache)]
    Store --> Serve
    Process --> DB[(Database)]
    DB --> Transform[Transform Data]
    Transform --> Response[/JSON Response/]
    Serve --> Response
    Response --> Log[Log Request]
    Log --> End([End])
    TooMany --> Log

    style Start fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style End fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style Error fill:#f44336,color:#fff
    style TooMany fill:#ff9800,color:#fff
    style DB fill:#2196F3,color:#fff
